710711f-a.text:

(2)  A later and more inclusive view.  Note the demolition of No.s 624 to 620.  That adjoined the corner structure, No. 626.

December 4, 1936.

(3)  Similar to No 2 and showing a further view eastward on the south side of W. 46th Street.

December 4, 1936
